<view class="commentWrap flex align-center">
    <view class="hotelScore margin-top margin-bottom flex align-center">
        <view class="avreageScore text-blue">
            <text>4.6</text>
            <text>分</text>
        </view>
        <view class="detailScore flex">
            <view class="scoreItem">
                <view>位置</view>
                <view class="itemProgress">
                    <progress percent="80" activeColor="#18A8EA" />
                </view>
                <view>4.5</view>
            </view>
            <view class="scoreItem">
                <view>卫生</view>
                <view class="itemProgress">
                    <progress percent="80" activeColor="#18A8EA" />
                </view>
                <view>4.5</view>
            </view>
            <view class="scoreItem">
                <view>设施</view>
                <view class="itemProgress">
                    <progress percent="80" activeColor="#18A8EA" />
                </view>
                <view>4.5</view>
            </view>
            <view class="scoreItem">
                <view>服务</view>
                <view class="itemProgress">
                    <progress percent="80" activeColor="#18A8EA" />
                </view>
                <view>4.5</view>
            </view>
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class="conmentTabTitle">
        <scroll-view scroll-x class="bg-white nav shadow">
            <view class="flex text-center">
                <view class="cu-item flex-sub {{index==TabCur?'text-blue cur':''}}" wx:for="{{commentTab}}" wx:key bindtap="tabSelect" data-id="{{index}}">
                {{commentTab[index]}}
                </view>
            </view>
        </scroll-view>
    </view>
    <view class="commentTabContent margin-top">
        <view class="commentTag flex justify-around">
            <view class="bg-blue">性价比高(5)</view>
            <view class="bg-ghostWhite">交通方便(13)</view>
            <view class="bg-ghostWhite">环境不错(8)</view>
            <view class="bg-ghostWhite">服务周到(3)</view>
        </view>
        <view class="commentList flex align-center">
            <view class="commentItem margin-top padding-bottom flex">
                <view class="commentTopInfo flex">
                    <view class="commentImg">
                        <image class="full-img round" src="https://www.youmuzhe.net/image/tx.jpg" />
                    </view>
                    <view>
                        <view class="userName text-bold">用户昵称</view>
                        <view class="starGroup flex justify-between align-center">
                            <icon class="cuIcon-favorfill text-orange" />
                            <icon class="cuIcon-favorfill text-orange" />
                            <icon class="cuIcon-favorfill text-orange" />
                            <icon class="cuIcon-favorfill text-orange" />
                            <icon class="cuIcon-favorfill text-gray" />
                        </view>
                    </view>
                </view>
                <view class="commentContent margin-bottom">
                    <view class="commentWord">
                        34层俯瞰贵阳半城，小雨绵绵中空气湿润舒服，相比北京雾霜，贵阳是天堂般的存在。大床软硬度很舒服，卫生间很大，服务606相应很及时。中餐厅菜品一般般，中规中矩，有张22人台，当晚一行人喝到酒酣耳热时8瓶茅台下肚，还是贵州的茅台顺滑适口不醉人啊！
